scism in Europe, \u201CThe end of the regime seemed near\u201D (1431).1"), mdx("p", null, "The regime had begun only two years earlier with the support of a vital constituency. Within days of becoming prime minister, Mussolini had taken immediate steps to make good on his promises to the church to restore its influence in Italian society. He had his new cabinet attend a Mass and ordered them to kneel (832)."));
